[
  {
    "startTime": 1.75,
    "endTime": 3.91,
    "text": "Our subject today is Simon McNeil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.91,
    "endTime": 7.35,
    "text": "He's a self-professed medium."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.35,
    "endTime": 10.74,
    "text": "He's almost here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.74,
    "endTime": 14.26,
    "text": "For those of you that don't know, I've recently lost my son Miles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.26,
    "endTime": 17.41,
    "text": "People like Simon like to prey on grief."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.41,
    "endTime": 19.45,
    "text": "Ready whenever you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.45,
    "endTime": 21.602,
    "text": "I need complete darkness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.602,
    "endTime": 23.09,
    "text": "Or rather they do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.43,
    "endTime": 47.79,
    "text": "All the dead have stories."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.79,
    "endTime": 51.8,
    "text": "There is a place where these horrors are transcribed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.8,
    "endTime": 56.04,
    "text": "I'm not sure where I'm going, but it felt like I was being followed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.04,
    "endTime": 58.65,
    "text": "We're headed to Ravermoore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.65,
    "endTime": 60.62,
    "text": "Is it a nice place?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.62,
    "endTime": 61.61,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.61,
    "endTime": 62.41,
    "text": "Here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.41,
    "endTime": 63.83,
    "text": "The dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.83,
    "endTime": 65.375,
    "text": "They are so much closer than you realize."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.68,
    "endTime": 72.84,
    "text": "I wasn't planning on stopping."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.84,
    "endTime": 74.435,
    "text": "I just think I'm really tired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.435,
    "endTime": 76.56,
    "text": "Come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.56,
    "endTime": 77.61,
    "text": "You're safe here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.3,
    "endTime": 85.09,
    "text": "I just have a thing with noises."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.09,
    "endTime": 86.42,
    "text": "It's neurological."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.42,
    "endTime": 89.08,
    "text": "Would've probably been better if I just didn't stop taking the meds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.348,
    "endTime": 105.16,
    "text": "[GASPING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.16,
    "endTime": 105.96,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.96,
    "endTime": 106.94,
    "text": "I'm so sorry, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.94,
    "endTime": 108.17,
    "text": "I didn't mean to startle you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.84,
    "endTime": 113.72,
    "text": "Man, some bad shit happened here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.72,
    "endTime": 117.96,
    "text": "Urban decay, that's what happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.96,
    "endTime": 121.74,
    "text": "We like to think everyone who stays here is family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.596,
    "endTime": 132.07,
    "text": "We all die."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.07,
    "endTime": 137.56,
    "text": "But sometimes the stories of our passing must be forever carved into our collective memory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.24,
    "endTime": 145.94,
    "text": "But all stories end here."
  }
]